We like the way the Q50 looks, and the fact it's a new upstart amongst the established Germans (and Lexus, lest we forget). It's comfortable and economical too, but (yes, there's a but) we're not sure all its systems add to its driving experience. In all likelihood you'll find your favourite one, and stay in it.
